dynRDFa

Class ExportableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • dynRDFa.ExportableModel

  • public class ExportableModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The ExportableModel class packs together all the information that the velocity engine and template need to consume in order to generate the RDFa enriched web pages. This includes an ArrayList of treeple objects (a treeple is a group of statements), the prefix mappings, the publications per year, and the type of web page that needs to be generated.

    magda
